title: Google Nexus 5X review: the peoples' Android phone?
text:

The Nexus 5X is the smaller and cheaper of Google’s new flagship Android 6.0 Marshmallow smartphones, and is billed as the phone for everyone. It has a great camera, fingerprint sensor and ... »
